  "response": "As of 2015, one of the best all-around fighter jets is widely considered to be the Lockheed Martin F-22 Raptor. Lauded for its advanced stealth capabilities, supermaneuverability, superior speed, and exceptional avionics, the F-22 is often regarded as top tier among fighter aircraft. Additionally, its versatility in both air-to-air and air-to-ground roles has made it a formidable asset in various combat scenarios.\n\nAnother contender that frequently earns high marks is the Lockheed Martin F-35 Lightning II. Designed with modern combat versatility in mind, the F-35 features advanced stealth, sensor fusion, and network connectivity which allow it to excel in multiple mission profiles.\n\nThese two aircraft are often cited as leading examples of advanced fighter technology around that time period.",
